linstaller (2.10.1-1) pulse; urgency=low

  * Added linstaller.frontends where store frontends core files.
  * core/:
    - ported cli_frontend to linstaller.frontends.cli
    - added frontend auto-discovery feature (default for 3.x modules)
    - pass the package path to Module
  * modules/:
    - Ported welcome and userhost to 3.x-style modules package structure.
  * debian/: new package linstaller-frontend-cli which ships the cli frontend.
  * setup.py: updated to install frontends and modules inst/front.
  * linstaller: moved the loop code to new function loop_modules().
  * linstaller: support "back" res (restarts a loop starting from the module
    before the current)
  * modules/update: translate "Updating APT cache..." string.
  * modules/: ported everything to 3.x, except widget_test.
  * core/module.py: onchroot support on Install (default == True).
    Specifies if the install phase should be done in chroot or not.

 -- Eugenio Paolantonio (g7) <me@medesimo.eu>  Thu, 29 Dec 2011 12:50:17 +0100

