linstaller (2.0.0~pre2-1) emily; urgency=low

  * linstaller: added ability to preseed from command-line;
  * core/config: support initial (file-less) configurations;
  * modules/widget_test: splitted tests; added sequence, progressbar_val,
    progressbar_sleep seeds;
  * core/module: support default items in cache().
  * modules/update: specify default when calling cache().
  * core/config: return booleans instead of strings if True, False or None.
    (not case-sensitive).
  * modules/*: some logic changes due to the above modification.
    swap (partdisks) and root (userhost) requires None to disable.
  * config/semplice: changed root = False to root = None, due to the change
    above.
  * modules/: added new clean module; cleans /etc/linstaller if custom
    configurations are manually shipped during an ipothetical remaster.
  * config/semplice-base: added the clean frontend to modules.

