linstaller (1.51.0~pre3-1) emily; urgency=low

  * partdisks: library: added is_disk() and device_sort() functions
  * partdisks: library: return_device() correctly works on freespace
    partitions.
  * partdisks: use device_sort() to return a sorted list of what we
    should commit.
  * partdisks: set touched in automatic partitioning.
  * partdisks: do not format if, in interactive editor, swap is selected
    but swap_noformat preseed is true.
  * partdisks: inst: in revert, check for key "partdisks.inst" AND if any,
    revert used.
  * partdisks: inst: fixed get of "changed".
  * partdisks: "Go back" is now fixed.
  * partdisks: do not clear touched and changes when returning to self.main()
  * partdisks: in main() reload structure, but not remove "useas".

 -- Eugenio Paolantonio (g7) <me@medesimo.eu>  Sat, 20 Aug 2011 11:31:04 +0200

